    <string name="about_howto_title">How to play</string>
    <string name="about_howto_1">Tap the Jumplings before they fall from the bottom of the screen. Don\'t let them fall, or you\'ll lose one life.</string>
    <string name="about_howto_2">Kill the Jumplings very quickly one after the other to score combos and gain extra points.</string>
    <string name="about_howto_red">Red Jumplings are cute</string>
    <string name="about_howto_orange">Orange ones last two taps</string>
    <string name="about_howto_yellow">The yellow ones split when you tap on them</string>
    <string name="about_howto_bomb">Do not explode the bombs. That is obvious&#8230;</string>
    <string name="about_howto_lifeup">Extra life power up!</string>
    <string name="about_howto_sable">Ninja sable powerup. When you got it you can swipe through the screen to kill them faster. Lasts only for some seconds.</string>
